3412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:44:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淨係睇呢啲產品個佣咁高，係咪真係用嚟做儲蓄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無得咁講<br />\n<br />\nFUND MANAGER夠高人工啦<br />\n<br />\n車行/百老匯SALES一樣有佣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n芬佬喺個Pool抽1-3%一年，唔鐘意仲有ETF揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢啲計劃，頭1-2食晒啲錢咁。<br />\n<br />\n1球係Fund，一年收1-3萬。<br />\n<br />\n月供$3,000計劃，第一年已抽走$36,000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買車買電器，都叫做有舊嘢。<br />\n<br />\n買呢啲計劃，得堆紙，仲要等回本，除非靠賣呢啲計劃為生，唔係都好難可以講到好說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f740af645439c00595dad04498c6d4a9f53c69","tid":484438,"uid":133412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇p記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買左5年plan 諗住退休用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真買嘅話，希望你遇到樂觀情景，最怕遇著悲劇情景。"},{"pid":"a3ba719420e5b36b85fc18b5075c1416f2076c52","tid":484438,"uid":133412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:47:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>完全唔識投資一味死草錢 想買份5年嘅儲蓄保 5年後拎舊錢幫補下首期 有冇邊個plan推薦？</blockquote><br />\n拎錢買股票</blockquote><br />\n跟你咁做，之後遇正97咁就仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意，但用呢啲計劃，一開始就仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d071f7273b93dabbb8d5f03c9c906513bf90086","tid":484438,"uid":133412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講回報就唔買saving plan la on 9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSaving 唔講回報，買個Plan嚟做乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b43c0a72a5de032ec9c00729f6cf7061645644","tid":484438,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:01:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講回報就唔買saving plan la on 9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSaving 唔講回報，買個Plan嚟做乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係 唔講回報d錢就咁放銀行唔好? 靈活好多倍tim"},{"pid":"b15f95cb352d144552e35b2f9a6f055853189f6f","tid":484438,"uid":44534,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"分散風險姐 其實有錢多既咪擺囉 但你話用黎做首期就唔會做長plan la 我就幫小朋友儲既 等佢18 歲番一兩翻利是錢 再每年升多8-9 個% 有哂交代啦<br />\n不過實有人話我打手⋯⋯<br />\n講到尾其實無閒錢就唔會咁買 儲首期就最白痴 你點知個市幾時跌 一跌你舊錢仲係份單度 又要等下一個浪"},{"pid":"35bfeb65f846d2ccbbd27edbe69c2b33109facb2","tid":484438,"uid":229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講回報就唔買saving plan la on 9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSaving 唔講回報，買個Plan嚟做乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係 唔講回報d錢就咁放銀行唔好? 靈活好多倍tim</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉 咁點解仲要講邊個saving plan 抵買？"},{"pid":"34a009bd4f253725eaec37f9e1e7a02e823c5cf3","tid":484438,"uid":133412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分散風險姐 其實有錢多既咪擺囉 但你話用黎做首期就唔會做長plan la 我就幫小朋友儲既 等佢18 歲番一兩翻利是錢 再每年升多8-9 個% 有哂交代啦<br />\n不過實有人話我打手⋯⋯<br />\n講到尾其實無閒錢就唔會咁買 儲首期就最白痴 你點知個市幾時跌 一跌你舊錢仲係份單度 又要等下一個浪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/202441_d895f8b75c3b1dfa7ee49247156e4d31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F202441_d895f8b75c3b1dfa7ee49247156e4d31.png&h=78ffc2e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完都唔知佢買緊咩，果3.2％派唔足的話，又唔知點解。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個巿呢幾年都叫旺，紅利都係得100%，仲要得25年正常情景預期得IRR3.2%，乜唔係賺多咗應該派多啲紅利？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見啲代理派唔足（例如啲悲劇情景50-60%）時，就話個巿唔好，到巿好果時，又無派番多啲去補番條數。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n輸就客戶硬食，贏就股東價息齊升，呢個係分散風險，係分散咗股東的投資風險落客戶的儲蓄計劃回報上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求其去搵隻中國銀行人Ｘ的2pay5都唔使咁麻煩，5年後保證15%走，5年後再睇吓個情況。<br />\n<br />\n用呢啲計劃，一焗就幾十年，宏Ｘ班投資團隊如果做得唔好，換唔到馬不突止，退保仲要蝕退保費，縛到死一死，為乜呢？啲錢擺喺銀行又唔會飛走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4bbec28bd56320f0f3baa4b56155ccd9156777","tid":484438,"uid":133412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講回報就唔買saving plan la on 9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSaving 唔講回報，買個Plan嚟做乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係 唔講回報d錢就咁放銀行唔好? 靈活好多倍tim</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉 咁點解仲要講邊個saving plan 抵買？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講緊點解唔抵賣，因為以儲蓄為名，但一個儲蓄計劃，一開始要等以十年計先可以回本的計劃，又要硬供一段長時間，又唔睇回報的話，買果個應該係身痕。"},{"pid":"f975d0e4b8709b4843c049572cd35faf0474da06","tid":484438,"uid":133412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:47:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講回報就唔買saving plan la on 9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSaving 唔講回報，買個Plan嚟做乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係 唔講回報d錢就咁放銀行唔好? 靈活好多倍tim</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買Saving Plan，係講佣金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e3c4f1fcc010cd8452211019e0e11a7d96bb61","tid":484438,"uid":229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T14:53:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講回報就唔買saving plan la on 9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSaving 唔講回報，買個Plan嚟做乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係 唔講回報d錢就咁放銀行唔好? 靈活好多倍tim</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉 咁點解仲要講邊個saving plan 抵買？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講緊點解唔抵賣，因為以儲蓄為名，但一個儲蓄計劃，一開始要等以十年計先可以回本的計劃，又要硬供一段長時間，又唔睇回報的話，買果個應該係身痕。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係既 <br />\n十年黎all in 700都賺個開<br />\n放銀行仲好<br />\n可以隨時拎走 <br />\n仲即刻回本添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ab560a7c65097c7f6538f60a5d9f04419ed58e","tid":484438,"uid":68993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:45:31.000Z","msg":"其實宏利d saving plan e家無邊隻撼得贏其他公司<br />\n<br />\n高紅利plan: Manuvision <br />\n歷史唔夠，為出而出既plan (定位同prudential 隻進升一樣)<br />\n宏利加左個唔知19幾年後可以拎一半e個option 去打進升<br />\n仲未計中人壽盈豐、AIA 簡愛e d plan <br />\n<br />\nCoupon plan: LaVie <br />\n出左好幾年，IRR 廢既plan <br />\ne家BOClife 隻綻放 會好過佢<br />\n或者拎黎sell 醫療融資e d 19野<br />\n<br />\n即期年金 / 長供年金: Manujoy / 理想入息計劃<br />\n有萬通，其他公司d 年金plan 都係可以收皮先<br />\n暫時見唔到有其他公司既年金夠萬通黎<br />\n<br />\n所以e家 宏利咪sell 果d 派息基金plan<br />\n因為上面堆plan 都比人打殘"},{"pid":"8007c7b5be7f60c4c0147231e0b0af3bb11369d8","tid":484438,"uid":68993,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:00:07.000Z","msg":"仲有，用分紅保險去計<br />\n<br />\nAIA 簡愛 可以lump sum pay (expect 5 年回本) <br />\nPrudential EGS 可以lump sum pay (expect 5 年回本)<br />\nMassmutual 年金可以lump sum pay (expect 4 年回本)<br />\n中人壽隻盈豐寶5年lump sum 個return 都追到下上面果d (expect 6 年回本)<br />\n<br />\n宏利d 分紅保險<br />\nLaVie, Manuvision, 理想入息計劃，宏譽<br />\n無一隻係有lump sum pay e個option 去比保戶提高回報<br />\n就算最短5年去供，比你預繳埋，頂盡都要第8年回本<br />\n<br />\n明唔明點解宏利d plan 廢係邊個位"},{"pid":"19b5481f4c062a104f24f5a83670c47a43bf8867","tid":484438,"uid":61206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:13:26.000Z","msg":"講多d宏X<br />\n有fd做緊見佢講到好好賺咁"}]}